  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Shooting and Rebounding</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/9b51a645ebd2a564b94e646d80870f7b.poster.avif?t=1683273861\" width=500 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/9b51a645ebd2a564b94e646d80870f7b.webm?t=1683273861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/9b51a645ebd2a564b94e646d80870f7b.mp4?t=1683273861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In this game, players can use blocking to rebound enemy bullets. Perfect rebounds will temporarily disable enemy attacks.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Jumping</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/b4da40fa23619a9e0f64d47d240adeeb.poster.avif?t=1683273861\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/b4da40fa23619a9e0f64d47d240adeeb.webm?t=1683273861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/b4da40fa23619a9e0f64d47d240adeeb.mp4?t=1683273861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use different routes to reach the destination.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cute and Healing Pixel Art Style</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/0ed7a172f8954266f17a61a515f1cbbe.poster.avif?t=1683273861\" width=500 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/0ed7a172f8954266f17a61a515f1cbbe.webm?t=1683273861\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386070/extras/0ed7a172f8954266f17a61a515f1cbbe.mp4?t=1683273861\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The use of pixel art style for the paper character is not just to save art resources!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Objective</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Defeat the final boss to open the exit of the maze.</li></ul>",
